{"tid":880460,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(分享) (Android專用) 將你既Telegram Stickers用落Whatsapp到","createTime":"2018-10-28T17:17:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-09T07:04:50.000Z","uid":103514,"like":18,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"42e8df62c61a2068e3c2c06dd5aa0e2cff39da84","tid":880460,"uid":103514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T17:17:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">以下Android專用</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n首先多謝 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/879789/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/879789/page/1</a> 入面 <span style=\"color: red;\">Chok巴</span>同<span style=\"color: red;\">DVD-writer</span>巴打 (仲有其他巴打)既分享，可以俾我地極速用到好多stickers<br />\n<br />\n自己做左成日伸手黨，岩岩試到可以將Telegram Stickers用落Whatsapp到，瞓前極速打個分享<br />\n<br />\n好簡單，十分鐘一定做完1 set<br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n例子<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RqhBBTc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRqhBBTc.jpg&h=bf56c48e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n需要工具:<br />\n1. 手機 (先下載 <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.dstukalov.walocalstoragestickers\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.dstukalov.walocalstoragestickers&d=kjhNQfrKxenTEj2ndVJapL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=901f525e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.dstukalov.walocalstoragestickers</a>) 鳴謝巴打 Froggy<br />\n2. 電腦版 Telegram (最好有，方便好多)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nStep:<br />\n1. 先係Telegram裝呢個bot <a href=\"https://telegram.me/stickerset2packbot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegram.me%2Fstickerset2packbot&d=kjhNQfrKxenTEj2ndVJapL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=085bcc06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://telegram.me/stickerset2packbot</a><br />\n用黎將啲sticker export做png圖片<br />\n<br />\n2. Copy你想要既telegram sticker既link (e.g. <a href=\"https://t.me/addstickers/fbicon\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Faddstickers%2Ffbicon&d=kjhNQfrKxenTEj2ndVJapL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=6cb504e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/addstickers/fbicon</a>)<br />\n可以係手機setting&gt;Stickers &amp; Maskers&gt; 每個sticker旁既三點搵到<br />\n<br />\n3. 打開頭先裝左既bot<br />\n<br />\n4. 跟住指示打command，最快既step係<br />\na.) /newpack<br />\nb.) paste 頭先條sticker link<br />\nc.) /finish png 160 <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">***唔打png既話default 係jpg, 用唔到的<br />\n***數字係image size，如果你個stickers本身好大，有機會要加大數值。靠各位自己慢慢試了</span><br />\nd.) 等待完成，之後會有一個zip file出左黎裝住晒所有png，解壓縮<br />\n<br />\n5. 開手機個apps &quot;Personal stickers for WhatsApp&quot;<br />\n<br />\n6. 理論上，個apps就會自動detect+食到晒所有岩岩既png圖片做stickers<br />\n<br />\n7. Add&gt;&gt;完成<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽朝返工<br />\n無詳細再試其他，希望幫到咁多位an狗(包括我)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d1b8b425eda4b1f39efee538c70dba15cb66bdd","tid":880460,"uid":103514,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T17:18:56.000Z","msg":"毒撚自推一下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32ea4d73a0bf930b65acb6ba5866324e6085e649","tid":880460,"uid":103514,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T17:26:08.000Z","msg":"<img sr