By":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T16:37:13.000Z","msg":"成功左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔該晒"},{"pid":"0c1b404b4d6e6af901e8feb15dc3f1a13fee80db","tid":880460,"uid":47627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T17:20:11.000Z","msg":"有無人同我一樣整完之後D圖全部都有個黑色底色係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"962bc6f1d5a12fbb13b17b3b01599265a67a95f7","tid":880460,"uid":103514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c1b404b4d6e6af901e8feb15dc3f1a13fee80db","tid":880460,"uid":47627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T17:20:11.000Z","msg":"有無人同我一樣整完之後D圖全部都有個黑色底色係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T00:50:29.000Z","msg":"可能係張圖嘅透明度有問題"},{"pid":"536029db32e64aecfde57b064b52e22ae2f94e0e","tid":880460,"uid":103514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T00:52:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Android專用</span></span><br />\n<br />\n更新: 30/10/2018<br />\n(更新Google play死link)<br />\n<br />\n將Telegram stickers轉去Whatsapp用<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n需要工具:<br />\n1. 手機 (先下載 <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.dstukalov.walocalstoragestickers\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.dstukalov.walocalstoragestickers&d=kjhNQfrKxenTEj2ndVJapL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=901f525e\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.dstukalov.walocalstoragestickers</a> )<br />\n2. 電腦版 Telegram (optional)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nStep:<br />\n1. 先係Telegram裝呢個bot <a href=\"https://telegram.me/stickerset2packbot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegram.me%2Fstickerset2packbot&d=kjhNQfrKxenTEj2ndVJapL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=085bcc06\" target=\"_blank\">https://telegram.me/stickerset2packbot</a><br />\n用黎將啲sticker export做png圖片/webp<br />\n<br />\n2. Copy你想要既telegram sticker既link (e.g. <a href=\"https://t.me/addstickers/fbicon\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Faddstickers%2Ffbicon&d=kjhNQfrKxenTEj2ndVJapL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=6cb504e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/addstickers/fbicon</a><br />\n可以係手機setting&gt;Stickers &amp; Maskers&gt; 每個sticker旁既三點搵到<br />\n<br />\n3. 打開頭先裝左既bot<br />\n<br />\n4. 跟住指示打command，最快既step係<br />\na.) /newpack<br />\nb.) paste 頭先條sticker link<br />\nc.) /finish png 160 <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">***唔打png既話default 係jpg, 用唔到的<br />\n***數字係image width size，如果你個stickers本身好大，有機會要加大數值。靠各位自己慢慢試了</span><br />\nd.) 等待完成，之後會有一個zip file出左黎裝住晒所有png，解壓縮<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">***巴打回饋: 張圖file size如果大過100kb都有機會喺add stickers時出error <br />\n***解壓完嘅folder，應該同時出現一個&quot;src&quot;嘅folder，入面嘅webp同樣可以用嚟出sticker，而且file size更細，相對無咁易error</span><br />\n<br />\n5. 開手機啱啱下載個apps &quot;Personal stickers for WhatsApp&quot;<br />\n<br />\n6. 理論上，個apps就會自動detect+食到晒所有岩岩既png圖片/webp做stickers<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">***建議所有stickers圖片放喺download下自己開嘅一個新嘅folder，入面自己做分類。Folder name應該就係sticker pack name<br />\n***Whatsapp問題，只能一pack食30個stickers。多於30，餘數請另開folders當另一pack處理<br />\n</span><br />\n7. Add&gt;&gt;完成<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">***Android whatsapp問題，如果你用其他巴打分享嘅apk/以上方法整，請勿del apps/移動圖片file path，因為會令到啲sticker load唔返</span>"},{"pid":"e75df59d2187282c34170957580bfe756337c76a","tid":880460,"uid":157617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T01:19:14.000Z","msg":"謝樓主<br />\nbtw係咪要用beta板WhatsApp先得"},{"pid":"6ca4808bcde7d23f0a47c9f560c6653bd4302a1d","tid":880460,"uid":68902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T01:23:04.000Z","msg":"Stickers 自訂名稱純粹只可以檔案總管度自己睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過好過無得用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-